{"tid":1647041,"cid":25,"subCid":0,"title":"［屌你咁撚CUTE］狗狗被樹熊誤認媽「搭便車」 無辜大眼望主人求救","createTime":"2019-10-11T14:47:12.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-12T11:15:30.000Z","uid":109136,"like":13,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"ef1992a4466325d488c5e8bb91a8f1519e7a213d","tid":1647041,"uid":109136,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T14:47:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://pgw.udn.com.tw/gw/photo.php?u=https://uc.udn.com.tw/photo/2019/10/11/99/6929414.png&amp;s=Y&amp;x=0&amp;y=6&amp;sw=1280&amp;sh=676&amp;exp=3600\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpgw.udn.com.tw%2Fgw%2Fphoto.php%3Fu%3Dhttps%3A%2F%2Fuc.udn.com.tw%2Fphoto%2F2019%2F10%2F11%2F99%2F6929414.png%26s%3DY%26x%3D0%26y%3D6%26sw%3D1280%26sh%3D676%26exp%3D3600&h=59b0fa85&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n這隻狗狗托尼被樹熊寶寶纏上甩不掉，只能無奈看著主人求救。<br />\n<br />\n有些動物在走累的時候會選擇趴在其他動物上「搭便車」，尤其是動物寶寶也可能會因為認錯父母，而死抓著其他動物不放。澳洲有一隻名叫托尼（Tony）的狗被一隻樹熊寶寶誤認成媽媽纏上，趴在牠的背上怎樣也甩不下來，而托尼的主人看到這可愛的一幕便立刻記錄了下來，許多網友看到後也大讚「好可愛」。<br />\n<br />\n根據「7news」的報導，6日早上在澳洲的阿得雷德山（Adelaide Hills）托尼的主人發現牠被一隻樹熊寶寶爬上了背，一開始托尼並沒有發現，直到牠看見樹熊，並試圖將牠甩下，但樹熊卻死命抓住托尼，並持續跳到牠背上，托尼只能無辜地看著主人，而在經歷了1分多鐘後，托尼的主人便將樹熊取下，而樹熊也自行爬回附近的樹上，去尋找媽媽。<br />\n<br />\n影片一出後，許多網友紛紛留言，「可憐的樹熊，牠需要一個新的媽媽。」、「好可愛的樹熊寶寶。」、「一旦被樹熊纏上，就很難叫牠下來了吧。」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?time_continue=155&amp;v=WWi1lSRKhIw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Ftime_continue%3D155%26v%3DWWi1lSRKhIw&d=bDN9RnBWsu2ZFehd%2BUm4uMsFuFiCHHua96MUfZSGoRU%3D&h=ce5ada1f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?time_continue=155&amp;v=WWi1lSRKhIw</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://udn.com/news/story/7470/4099095\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fudn.com%2Fnews%2Fstory%2F7470%2F4099095&d=bDN9RnBWsu2ZFehd%2BUm4uMsFuFiCHHua96MUfZSGoRU%3D&h=e4161364\" target=\"_blank\">https://udn.com/news/story/7470/4099095</a>"},{"pid":"1fff04dcb1c42d0e39685b4288df6f83eca07b30","tid":1647041,"uid":90820,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T15:32:40.000Z","msg":"今次樓主唔貼埋自己<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"684d01da65b94e503b891a45c35e8caa6b8334b1","tid":1647041,"uid":109136,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"1fff04dcb1c42d0e39685b4288df6f83eca07b30","tid":1647041,"uid":90820,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T15:32:40.000Z","msg":"今次樓主唔貼埋自己<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T15:37:15.000Z","msg":"唔貼了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/GPWMHAo.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGPWMHAo.jpg&h=6030dbf4&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a30c1bec9742beac431d398776e3d938504c0a72","tid":1647041,"uid":109136,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T11:15:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/AimpAN7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAimpAN7.jpg&h=a091a393&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n推"}]}